#. lang="pli"><section class="sutta" id="thag19.1"><article><div
#. class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "thag19.1:1.1"
msgid "Theragāthā"
msgstr "Verses of the Senior Monks"

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "thag19.1:2.1"
msgid "Paññāsanipāta"
msgstr "The Book of the Fifties"

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "thag19.1:3.1"
msgid "Paṭhamavagga"
msgstr "Chapter One"

#. HTML: </p><h1>
msgctxt "thag19.1:4.1"
msgid "19.1. Tālapuṭattheragāthā"
msgstr "19.1. Tālapuṭa"

#. </h1></div><blockquote class="gatha"><p><a class="sc" id="1"></a><a
#. class="vns" id="vns1094"></a><a class="vnp" id="vnp1091"></a><a class="pts"
#. id="pts97"></a>
msgctxt "thag19.1:5.1"
msgid "“Kadā nuhaṃ pabbatakandarāsu,"
msgstr "Oh, when will I stay in a mountain cave,"

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "thag19.1:5.2"
msgid "Ekākiyo addutiyo vihassaṃ;"
msgstr "alone, with no companion,"

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "thag19.1:5.3"
msgid "Aniccato sabbabhavaṃ vipassaṃ,"
msgstr "discerning all states of existence as impermanent?"

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "thag19.1:5.4"
msgid "Taṃ me idaṃ taṃ nu kadā bhavissati."
msgstr "This hope of mine, when will it be?"

#. HTML: </p><p><a class="sc" id="2"></a><a class="vns" id="vns1095"></a><a
#. class="vnp" id="vnp1092"></a>
msgctxt "thag19.1:6.1"
msgid "Kadā nuhaṃ bhinnapaṭandharo muni,"
msgstr "Oh, when will I stay happily in the forest,"

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "thag19.1:6.2"
msgid "Kāsāvavattho amamo nirāso;"
msgstr "a sage wearing a torn robe, dressed in ocher,"

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "thag19.1:6.3"
msgid "Rāgañca dosañca tatheva mohaṃ,"
msgstr "unselfish, without desire,"

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "thag19.1:6.4"
msgid "Hantvā sukhī pavanagato vihassaṃ."
msgstr "with greed, hate, and delusion destroyed?"

#. HTML: </p><p><a class="sc" id="3"></a><a class="vns" id="vns1096"></a><a
#. class="vnp" id="vnp1093"></a>
msgctxt "thag19.1:7.1"
msgid "Kadā aniccaṃ vadharoganīḷaṃ,"
msgstr "Oh, when will I stay alone in the wood,"

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "thag19.1:7.2"
msgid "Kāyaṃ imaṃ maccujarāyupaddutaṃ;"
msgstr "fearless, discerning this body as impermanent,"

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "thag19.1:7.3"
msgid "Vipassamāno vītabhayo vihassaṃ,"
msgstr "a nest of death and disease,"

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "thag19.1:7.4"
msgid "Eko vane taṃ nu kadā bhavissati."
msgstr "oppressed by death and old age; when will it be?"

#. HTML: </p><p><a class="sc" id="4"></a><a class="vns" id="vns1097"></a><a
#. class="vnp" id="vnp1094"></a>
msgctxt "thag19.1:8.1"
msgid "Kadā nuhaṃ bhayajananiṃ dukhāvahaṃ,"
msgstr "Oh, when will I live, having grasped the sharp sword of wisdom"

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "thag19.1:8.2"
msgid "Taṇhālataṃ bahuvidhānuvattaniṃ;"
msgstr "and cut the creeper of craving that tangles around everything,"

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "thag19.1:8.3"
msgid "Paññāmayaṃ tikhiṇamasiṃ gahetvā,"
msgstr "the mother of fear, the bringer of suffering?"

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "thag19.1:8.4"
msgid "Chetvā vase tampi kadā bhavissati."
msgstr "When will it be?"

#. HTML: </p><p><a class="sc" id="5"></a><a class="vns" id="vns1098"></a><a
#. class="vnp" id="vnp1095"></a>
msgctxt "thag19.1:9.1"
msgid "Kadā nu paññāmayamuggatejaṃ,"
msgstr "Oh, when will I, seated on the lion’s throne,"

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "thag19.1:9.2"
msgid "Satthaṃ isīnaṃ sahasādiyitvā;"
msgstr "swiftly grasp the sword of the sages,"

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "thag19.1:9.3"
msgid "Māraṃ sasenaṃ sahasā bhañjissaṃ,"
msgstr "forged by wisdom, of fiery might,"

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "thag19.1:9.4"
msgid "Sīhāsane taṃ nu kadā bhavissati."
msgstr "and swiftly break Māra and his army? When will it be?"

#. HTML: </p><p><a class="sc" id="6"></a><a class="vns" id="vns1099"></a><a
#. class="vnp" id="vnp1096"></a>
msgctxt "thag19.1:10.1"
msgid "Kadā nuhaṃ sabbhi samāgamesu,"
msgstr "Oh, when will I be seen striving in the assemblies"

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "thag19.1:10.2"
msgid "Diṭṭho bhave dhammagarūhi tādibhi;"
msgstr "by those who are virtuous, poised, respecting the Dhamma,"

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "thag19.1:10.3"
msgid "Yāthāvadassīhi jitindriyehi,"
msgstr "seeing things as they are, with faculties subdued?"

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "thag19.1:10.4"
msgid "Padhāniyo taṃ nu kadā bhavissati."
msgstr "When will it be?"

#. HTML: </p><p><a class="sc" id="7"></a><a class="vns" id="vns1100"></a><a
#. class="vnp" id="vnp1097"></a>
msgctxt "thag19.1:11.1"
msgid "Kadā nu maṃ tandi khudā pipāsā,"
msgstr "Oh, when will I focus on my own goal on Giribbaja mountain,"

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "thag19.1:11.2"
msgid "Vātātapā kīṭasarīsapā vā;"
msgstr "free of oppression by laziness, hunger, thirst,"

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "thag19.1:11.3"
msgid "Na bādhayissanti na taṃ giribbaje,"
msgstr "wind, heat, insects, and reptiles?"

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "thag19.1:11.4"
msgid "Atthatthiyaṃ taṃ nu kadā bhavissati."
msgstr "When will it be?"

#. HTML: </p><p><a class="sc" id="8"></a><a class="vns" id="vns1101"></a><a
#. class="vnp" id="vnp1098"></a><a class="pts" id="pts98"></a>
msgctxt "thag19.1:12.1"
msgid "Kadā nu kho yaṃ viditaṃ mahesinā,"
msgstr "Oh, when will I, serene and mindful,"

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "thag19.1:12.2"
msgid "Cattāri saccāni sududdasāni;"
msgstr "understand the four truths,"

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "thag19.1:12.3"
msgid "Samāhitatto satimā agacchaṃ,"
msgstr "that were realized by the great hermit,"

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "thag19.1:12.4"
msgid "Paññāya taṃ taṃ nu kadā bhavissati."
msgstr "and are so very hard to see? When will it be?"

#. HTML: </p><p><a class="sc" id="9"></a><a class="vns" id="vns1102"></a><a
#. class="vnp" id="vnp1099"></a>
msgctxt "thag19.1:13.1"
msgid "Kadā nu rūpe amite ca sadde,"
msgstr "Oh, when will I, devoted to serenity,"

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "thag19.1:13.2"
msgid "Gandhe rase phusitabbe ca dhamme;"
msgstr "see with understanding the infinite sights,"

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "thag19.1:13.3"
msgid "Ādittatohaṃ samathehi yutto,"
msgstr "sounds, smells, tastes, touches, and thoughts"

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "thag19.1:13.4"
msgid "Paññāya dacchaṃ tadidaṃ kadā me."
msgstr "as burning? When will it be?"

#. HTML: </p><p><a class="sc" id="10"></a><a class="vns" id="vns1103"></a><a
#. class="vnp" id="vnp1100"></a>
msgctxt "thag19.1:14.1"
msgid "Kadā nuhaṃ dubbacanena vutto,"
msgstr "Oh, when will I not be downcast"

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "thag19.1:14.2"
msgid "Tato nimittaṃ vimano na hessaṃ;"
msgstr "because of criticism,"

#. HTML: <br>
#. VAR: pasatthopi → pasaṭṭhopi (s2, s3, pts1)
msgctxt "thag19.1:14.3"
msgid "Atho pasatthopi tato nimittaṃ,"
msgstr "nor elated because of praise?"

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "thag19.1:14.4"
msgid "Tuṭṭho na hessaṃ tadidaṃ kadā me."
msgstr "When will it be?"

#. HTML: </p><p><a class="sc" id="11"></a><a class="vns" id="vns1104"></a><a
#. class="vnp" id="vnp1101"></a>
msgctxt "thag19.1:15.1"
msgid "Kadā nu kaṭṭhe ca tiṇe latā ca,"
msgstr "Oh when will I discern the aggregates"

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "thag19.1:15.2"
msgid "Khandhe imehaṃ amite ca dhamme;"
msgstr "and the infinite varieties of phenomena,"

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "thag19.1:15.3"
msgid "Ajjhattikāneva ca bāhirāni ca,"
msgstr "both internal and external, as no more than"

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "thag19.1:15.4"
msgid "Samaṃ tuleyyaṃ tadidaṃ kadā me."
msgstr "wood, grass, and creepers? When will it be?"

#. HTML: </p><p><a class="sc" id="12"></a><a class="vns" id="vns1105"></a><a
#. class="vnp" id="vnp1102"></a>
msgctxt "thag19.1:16.1"
msgid "Kadā nu maṃ pāvusakālamegho,"
msgstr "Oh, when will the winter clouds pour down in season"

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "thag19.1:16.2"
msgid "Navena toyena sacīvaraṃ vane;"
msgstr "as I wear my robe in the forest,"

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "thag19.1:16.3"
msgid "Isippayātamhi pathe vajantaṃ,"
msgstr "walking the path trodden by the sages?"

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "thag19.1:16.4"
msgid "Ovassate taṃ nu kadā bhavissati."
msgstr "When will it be?"

#. HTML: </p><p><a class="sc" id="13"></a><a class="vns" id="vns1106"></a><a
#. class="vnp" id="vnp1103"></a>
msgctxt "thag19.1:17.1"
msgid "Kadā mayūrassa sikhaṇḍino vane,"
msgstr "Oh, when will I rise up, intent on attaining the deathless,"

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "thag19.1:17.2"
msgid "Dijassa sutvā girigabbhare rutaṃ;"
msgstr "hearing, in the mountain cave,"

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "thag19.1:17.3"
msgid "Paccuṭṭhahitvā amatassa pattiyā,"
msgstr "the cry of the crested peacock in the forest?"

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "thag19.1:17.4"
msgid "Sañcintaye taṃ nu kadā bhavissati."
msgstr "When will it be?"

#. HTML: </p><p><a class="sc" id="14"></a><a class="vns" id="vns1107"></a><a
#. class="vnp" id="vnp1104"></a>
msgctxt "thag19.1:18.1"
msgid "Kadā nu gaṅgaṃ yamunaṃ sarassatiṃ,"
msgstr "Oh, when will I cross the Ganges, Yamunā,"

#. HTML: <br>
#. VAR: vaḷavāmukhañca → baḷavāmukhañca (pts1-2) | balavāmukhañca (mr)
msgctxt "thag19.1:18.2"
msgid "Pātālakhittaṃ vaḷavāmukhañca;"
msgstr "and Sarasvatī rivers, the Pātāla country,"

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "thag19.1:18.3"
msgid "Asajjamāno patareyyamiddhiyā,"
msgstr "and the dangerous Baḷavāmukha sea,"

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "thag19.1:18.4"
msgid "Vibhiṃsanaṃ taṃ nu kadā bhavissati."
msgstr "by psychic power, without hindrance? When will it be?"

#. HTML: </p><p><a class="sc" id="15"></a><a class="vns" id="vns1108"></a><a
#. class="vnp" id="vnp1105"></a>
#. VAR: asaṅgacārī → saṅgāmacārī (s2, s3, pts1)
msgctxt "thag19.1:19.1"
msgid "Kadā nu nāgova asaṅgacārī,"
msgstr "Oh, when will I be devoted to absorption,"

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "thag19.1:19.2"
msgid "Padālaye kāmaguṇesu chandaṃ;"
msgstr "rejecting entirely the signs of beauty,"

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "thag19.1:19.3"
msgid "Nibbajjayaṃ sabbasubhaṃ nimittaṃ,"
msgstr "splitting apart desire for sensual stimulation,"

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "thag19.1:19.4"
msgid "Jhāne yuto taṃ nu kadā bhavissati."
msgstr "like an elephant that wanders free of ties? When will it be?"

#. HTML: </p><p><a class="sc" id="16"></a><a class="vns" id="vns1109"></a><a
#. class="vnp" id="vnp1106"></a><a class="pts" id="pts99"></a>
#. VAR: daliddako → daḷiddako (bj, pts1-2)
msgctxt "thag19.1:20.1"
msgid "Kadā iṇaṭṭova daliddako nidhiṃ,"
msgstr "Oh, when will I realize the teaching of the great hermit"

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "thag19.1:20.2"
msgid "Ārādhayitvā dhanikehi pīḷito;"
msgstr "and be content, like a poor person in debt,"

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "thag19.1:20.3"
msgid "Tuṭṭho bhavissaṃ adhigamma sāsanaṃ,"
msgstr "harassed by creditors, who finds a hidden treasure?"

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "thag19.1:20.4"
msgid "Mahesino taṃ nu kadā bhavissati."
msgstr "When will it be?"

#. HTML: </p><p><a class="sc" id="17"></a><a class="vns" id="vns1110"></a><a
#. class="vnp" id="vnp1107"></a>
msgctxt "thag19.1:21.1"
msgid "Bahūni vassāni tayāmhi yācito,"
msgstr "For many years you begged me,"

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "thag19.1:21.2"
msgid "‘Agāravāsena alaṃ nu te idaṃ’;"
msgstr "“Enough of living in a house for you!”"

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "thag19.1:21.3"
msgid "Taṃ dāni maṃ pabbajitaṃ samānaṃ,"
msgstr "Why do you not urge me on, mind,"

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "thag19.1:21.4"
msgid "Kiṃkāraṇā citta tuvaṃ na yuñjasi."
msgstr "now that I’ve gone forth as an ascetic?"

#. HTML: </p><p><a class="sc" id="18"></a><a class="vns" id="vns1111"></a><a
#. class="vnp" id="vnp1108"></a>
msgctxt "thag19.1:22.1"
msgid "Nanu ahaṃ citta tayāmhi yācito,"
msgstr "Didn’t you entice me, mind:"

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "thag19.1:22.2"
msgid "‘Giribbaje citrachadā vihaṅgamā’;"
msgstr "“On Giribbaja, the birds with colorful wings,"

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "thag19.1:22.3"
msgid "Mahindaghosatthanitābhigajjino,"
msgstr "greeting the thunder, Mahinda’s voice,"

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "thag19.1:22.4"
msgid "Te taṃ ramessanti vanamhi jhāyinaṃ."
msgstr "will delight you as you meditate in the forest?”"

#. HTML: </p><p><a class="sc" id="19"></a><a class="vns" id="vns1112"></a><a
#. class="vnp" id="vnp1109"></a>
msgctxt "thag19.1:23.1"
msgid "Kulamhi mitte ca piye ca ñātake,"
msgstr "\"In my family circle, friends, loved ones, and relatives;"

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "thag19.1:23.2"
msgid "Khiḍḍāratiṃ kāmaguṇañca loke;"
msgstr "and in the world, sports and play, and sensual pleasures;"

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "thag19.1:23.3"
msgid "Sabbaṃ pahāya imamajjhupāgato,"
msgstr "all these I gave up when I entered this life:"

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "thag19.1:23.4"
msgid "Athopi tvaṃ citta na mayha tussasi."
msgstr "and even then you’re not content with me, mind!"

#. HTML: </p><p><a class="sc" id="20"></a><a class="vns" id="vns1113"></a><a
#. class="vnp" id="vnp1110"></a>
msgctxt "thag19.1:24.1"
msgid "Mameva etaṃ na hi tvaṃ paresaṃ,"
msgstr "This is mine alone, it doesn’t belong to others;"

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "thag19.1:24.2"
msgid "Sannāhakāle paridevitena kiṃ;"
msgstr "when it is time to don your armor, why lament?"

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "thag19.1:24.3"
msgid "Sabbaṃ idaṃ calamiti pekkhamāno,"
msgstr "Reflecting that all this is unstable,"

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "thag19.1:24.4"
msgid "Abhinikkhamiṃ amatapadaṃ jigīsaṃ."
msgstr "I went forth, longing for the deathless state."

#. HTML: </p><p><a class="sc" id="21"></a><a class="vns" id="vns1114"></a><a
#. class="vnp" id="vnp1111"></a>
msgctxt "thag19.1:25.1"
msgid "Suyuttavādī dvipadānamuttamo,"
msgstr "The methodical teacher, supreme among people,"

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "thag19.1:25.2"
msgid "Mahābhisakko naradammasārathi;"
msgstr "great physician, guide for those who wish to train, said:"

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "thag19.1:25.3"
msgid "‘Cittaṃ calaṃ makkaṭasannibhaṃ iti,"
msgstr "“The mind fidgets like a monkey,"

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "thag19.1:25.4"
msgid "Avītarāgena sudunnivārayaṃ’."
msgstr "so it’s very hard to control if you are not free of lust.”"

#. HTML: </p><p><a class="sc" id="22"></a><a class="vns" id="vns1115"></a><a
#. class="vnp" id="vnp1112"></a>
msgctxt "thag19.1:26.1"
msgid "Kāmā hi citrā madhurā manoramā,"
msgstr "Sensual pleasures are diverse, sweet, delightful;"

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "thag19.1:26.2"
msgid "Aviddasū yattha sitā puthujjanā;"
msgstr "an ignorant ordinary person is bound to them."

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "thag19.1:26.3"
msgid "Te dukkhamicchanti punabbhavesino,"
msgstr "Seeking to be reborn again, they wish for suffering;"

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "thag19.1:26.4"
msgid "Cittena nītā niraye nirākatā."
msgstr "led on by their mind, they’re relegated to hell."

#. HTML: </p><p><a class="sc" id="23"></a><a class="vns" id="vns1116"></a><a
#. class="vnp" id="vnp1113"></a>
msgctxt "thag19.1:27.1"
msgid "‘Mayūrakoñcābhirutamhi kānane,"
msgstr "“Staying in the grove resounding with cries"

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "thag19.1:27.2"
msgid "Dīpīhi byagghehi purakkhato vasaṃ;"
msgstr "of peacocks and herons, and honored by leopards and tigers,"

#. HTML: <br>
#. VAR: virādhaya → padhāraya (s2, s3) | virāye (pts1)
msgctxt "thag19.1:27.3"
msgid "Kāye apekkhaṃ jaha mā virādhaya’,"
msgstr "abandon concern for the body, without fail!”"

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "thag19.1:27.4"
msgid "Itissu maṃ citta pure niyuñjasi."
msgstr "So you used to urge me, mind."

#. HTML: </p><p><a class="sc" id="24"></a><a class="vns" id="vns1117"></a><a
#. class="vnp" id="vnp1114"></a><a class="pts" id="pts100"></a>
msgctxt "thag19.1:28.1"
msgid "‘Bhāvehi jhānāni ca indriyāni ca,"
msgstr "“Develop the absorptions and spiritual faculties,"

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "thag19.1:28.2"
msgid "Balāni bojjhaṅgasamādhibhāvanā;"
msgstr "the powers, awakening factors, and immersion;"

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "thag19.1:28.3"
msgid "Tisso ca vijjā phusa buddhasāsane’,"
msgstr "realize the three knowledges in the teaching of the Buddha!”"

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "thag19.1:28.4"
msgid "Itissu maṃ citta pure niyuñjasi."
msgstr "So you used to urge me, mind."

#. HTML: </p><p><a class="sc" id="25"></a><a class="vns" id="vns1118"></a><a
#. class="vnp" id="vnp1115"></a>
msgctxt "thag19.1:29.1"
msgid "‘Bhāvehi maggaṃ amatassa pattiyā,"
msgstr "“Develop the eightfold path for realizing the deathless,"

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "thag19.1:29.2"
msgid "Niyyānikaṃ sabbadukhakkhayogadhaṃ;"
msgstr "emancipating, plunging into the end of all suffering,"

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "thag19.1:29.3"
msgid "Aṭṭhaṅgikaṃ sabbakilesasodhanaṃ’,"
msgstr "and cleansing all defilements!”"

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "thag19.1:29.4"
msgid "Itissu maṃ citta pure niyuñjasi."
msgstr "So you used to urge me, mind."

#. HTML: </p><p><a class="sc" id="26"></a><a class="vns" id="vns1119"></a><a
#. class="vnp" id="vnp1116"></a>
msgctxt "thag19.1:30.1"
msgid "‘Dukkhanti khandhe paṭipassa yoniso,"
msgstr "“Reflect properly on the aggregates as suffering,"

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "thag19.1:30.2"
msgid "Yato ca dukkhaṃ samudeti taṃ jaha;"
msgstr "and abandon that from which suffering arises;"

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "thag19.1:30.3"
msgid "Idheva dukkhassa karohi antaṃ’,"
msgstr "make an end of suffering in this very life!”"

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "thag19.1:30.4"
msgid "Itissu maṃ citta pure niyuñjasi."
msgstr "So you used to urge me, mind."

#. HTML: </p><p><a class="sc" id="27"></a><a class="vns" id="vns1120"></a><a
#. class="vnp" id="vnp1117"></a>
msgctxt "thag19.1:31.1"
msgid "‘Aniccaṃ dukkhanti vipassa yoniso,"
msgstr "“Properly discern that impermanence is suffering,"

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "thag19.1:31.2"
msgid "Suññaṃ anattāti aghaṃ vadhanti ca;"
msgstr "that emptiness is non-self, and that misery is death."

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "thag19.1:31.3"
msgid "Manovicāre uparundha cetaso’,"
msgstr "Uproot the wandering mind!”"

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "thag19.1:31.4"
msgid "Itissu maṃ citta pure niyuñjasi."
msgstr "So you used to urge me, mind."

#. HTML: </p><p><a class="sc" id="28"></a><a class="vns" id="vns1121"></a><a
#. class="vnp" id="vnp1118"></a>
msgctxt "thag19.1:32.1"
msgid "‘Muṇḍo virūpo abhisāpamāgato,"
msgstr "“Bald, unsightly, accursed,"

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "thag19.1:32.2"
msgid "Kapālahatthova kulesu bhikkhasu;"
msgstr "seek alms amongst families, bowl in hand."

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "thag19.1:32.3"
msgid "Yuñjassu satthuvacane mahesino’,"
msgstr "Devote yourself to the word of the teacher, the great hermit!”"

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "thag19.1:32.4"
msgid "Itissu maṃ citta pure niyuñjasi."
msgstr "So you used to urge me, mind."

#. HTML: </p><p><a class="sc" id="29"></a><a class="vns" id="vns1122"></a><a
#. class="vnp" id="vnp1119"></a>
#. VAR: visikhantare → visakhantaraṃ (s2, s3, pts1)
msgctxt "thag19.1:33.1"
msgid "‘Susaṃvutatto visikhantare caraṃ,"
msgstr "“Wander the streets well-restrained,"

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "thag19.1:33.2"
msgid "Kulesu kāmesu asaṅgamānaso;"
msgstr "unattached to families and sensual pleasures,"

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "thag19.1:33.3"
msgid "Cando yathā dosinapuṇṇamāsiyā’,"
msgstr "like the full moon on a bright night!”"

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "thag19.1:33.4"
msgid "Itissu maṃ citta pure niyuñjasi."
msgstr "So you used to urge me, mind."

#. HTML: </p><p><a class="sc" id="30"></a><a class="vns" id="vns1123"></a><a
#. class="vnp" id="vnp1120"></a>
#. VAR: hohi → hoti (s2, s3, pts1)
msgctxt "thag19.1:34.1"
msgid "‘Āraññiko hohi ca piṇḍapātiko,"
msgstr "“Be a wilderness-dweller and an alms-eater,"

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "thag19.1:34.2"
msgid "Sosāniko hohi ca paṃsukūliko;"
msgstr "one who lives in charnel grounds, a rag-robe wearer,"

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "thag19.1:34.3"
msgid "Nesajjiko hohi sadā dhute rato’,"
msgstr "one who never lies down, always delighting in ascetic practices.”"

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "thag19.1:34.4"
msgid "Itissu maṃ citta pure niyuñjasi."
msgstr "So you used to urge me, mind."

#. HTML: </p><p><a class="sc" id="31"></a><a class="vns" id="vns1124"></a><a
#. class="vnp" id="vnp1121"></a>
msgctxt "thag19.1:35.1"
msgid "Ropetva rukkhāni yathā phalesī,"
msgstr "Mind, when you urge me to the impermanent and unstable,"

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "thag19.1:35.2"
msgid "Mūle taruṃ chettu tameva icchasi;"
msgstr "you’re acting like someone who plants trees,"

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "thag19.1:35.3"
msgid "Tathūpamaṃ cittamidaṃ karosi,"
msgstr "then, when they’re about to fruit,"

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "thag19.1:35.4"
msgid "Yaṃ maṃ aniccamhi cale niyuñjasi."
msgstr "wishes to cut down the very same trees."

#. HTML: </p><p><a class="sc" id="32"></a><a class="vns" id="vns1125"></a><a
#. class="vnp" id="vnp1122"></a>
msgctxt "thag19.1:36.1"
msgid "Arūpa dūraṅgama ekacāri,"
msgstr "Incorporeal mind, far-traveler, lone-wanderer:"

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "thag19.1:36.2"
msgid "Na te karissaṃ vacanaṃ idānihaṃ;"
msgstr "I won’t do your bidding any more."

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "thag19.1:36.3"
msgid "Dukkhā hi kāmā kaṭukā mahabbhayā,"
msgstr "Sensual pleasures are suffering, painful, and very dangerous;"

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "thag19.1:36.4"
msgid "Nibbānamevābhimano carissaṃ."
msgstr "I’ll wander with my mind focused only on quenching."

#. HTML: </p><p><a class="sc" id="33"></a><a class="vns" id="vns1126"></a><a
#. class="vnp" id="vnp1123"></a>
msgctxt "thag19.1:37.1"
msgid "Nāhaṃ alakkhyā ahirikkatāya vā,"
msgstr "I didn’t go forth due to bad luck or shamelessness,"

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "thag19.1:37.2"
msgid "Na cittahetū na ca dūrakantanā;"
msgstr "or due to a whim or banishment,"

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "thag19.1:37.3"
msgid "Ājīvahetū ca ahaṃ na nikkhamiṃ,"
msgstr "nor for the sake of a livelihood;"

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "thag19.1:37.4"
msgid "Kato ca te citta paṭissavo mayā."
msgstr "it was because I agreed to the promise you made, mind."

#. HTML: </p><p><a class="sc" id="34"></a><a class="vns" id="vns1127"></a><a
#. class="vnp" id="vnp1124"></a><a class="pts" id="pts101"></a>
msgctxt "thag19.1:38.1"
msgid "‘Appicchatā sappurisehi vaṇṇitā,"
msgstr "“Having few wishes, abandoning disparagement,"

#. HTML: <br>
#. VAR: vupasamo dukhassa → vūpasamo dukkhassa (bj, s2, s3)
msgctxt "thag19.1:38.2"
msgid "Makkhappahānaṃ vupasamo dukhassa’;"
msgstr "the stilling of suffering: these are praised by good people.”"

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "thag19.1:38.3"
msgid "Itissu maṃ citta tadā niyuñjasi,"
msgstr "So you used to urge me, mind,"

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "thag19.1:38.4"
msgid "Idāni tvaṃ gacchasi pubbaciṇṇaṃ."
msgstr "but now you keep on with your old habits!"

#. HTML: </p><p><a class="sc" id="35"></a><a class="vns" id="vns1128"></a><a
#. class="vnp" id="vnp1125"></a>
#. VAR: Taṇhā avijjā → taṇhaṃ virajjañca (s2, s3) | taṇhaṃ avijjañca (pts1)
msgctxt "thag19.1:39.1"
msgid "Taṇhā avijjā ca piyāpiyañca,"
msgstr "Craving, ignorance, the loved and unloved,"

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "thag19.1:39.2"
msgid "Subhāni rūpāni sukhā ca vedanā;"
msgstr "pretty sights, pleasant feelings,"

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "thag19.1:39.3"
msgid "Manāpiyā kāmaguṇā ca vantā,"
msgstr "and the delightful kinds of sensual stimulation:"

#. HTML: <br>
#. VAR: āvamituṃ → āvasituṃ (s2, s3) | āgamituṃ (pts1)
msgctxt "thag19.1:39.4"
msgid "Vante ahaṃ āvamituṃ na ussahe."
msgstr "I’ve vomited them all, and I won’t swallow them back."

#. HTML: </p><p><a class="sc" id="36"></a><a class="vns" id="vns1129"></a><a
#. class="vnp" id="vnp1126"></a>
msgctxt "thag19.1:40.1"
msgid "Sabbattha te citta vaco kataṃ mayā,"
msgstr "I’ve done your bidding everywhere, mind!"

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "thag19.1:40.2"
msgid "Bahūsu jātīsu na mesi kopito;"
msgstr "For many births, I’ve done nothing to upset you,"

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "thag19.1:40.3"
msgid "Ajjhattasambhavo kataññutāya te,"
msgstr "yet this self-made chain is your show of gratitude!"

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "thag19.1:40.4"
msgid "Dukkhe ciraṃ saṃsaritaṃ tayā kate."
msgstr "For a long time I’ve transmigrated in the suffering you’ve created."

#. HTML: </p><p><a class="sc" id="37"></a><a class="vns" id="vns1130"></a><a
#. class="vnp" id="vnp1127"></a>
#. VAR: brāhmaṇo → brāhmaṇe (pts2) | brāhmaṇaṃ (?)
msgctxt "thag19.1:41.1"
msgid "Tvaññeva no citta karosi brāhmaṇo,"
msgstr "Only you, mind, make a brahmin;"

#. HTML: <br>
#. VAR: rājadasī → rājādisī (s2, s3, mr) | rājadisī (pts1-2)
msgctxt "thag19.1:41.2"
msgid "Tvaṃ khattiyo rājadasī karosi;"
msgstr "you make an aristocrat or a royal hermit."

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "thag19.1:41.3"
msgid "Vessā ca suddā ca bhavāma ekadā,"
msgstr "Sometimes we become traders or workers;"

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "thag19.1:41.4"
msgid "Devattanaṃ vāpi taveva vāhasā."
msgstr "and life as a god is also on account of you."

#. HTML: </p><p><a class="sc" id="38"></a><a class="vns" id="vns1131"></a><a
#. class="vnp" id="vnp1128"></a>
msgctxt "thag19.1:42.1"
msgid "Taveva hetū asurā bhavāmase,"
msgstr "You alone make us demons;"

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "thag19.1:42.2"
msgid "Tvaṃmūlakaṃ nerayikā bhavāmase;"
msgstr "because of you we’re born in hell."

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "thag19.1:42.3"
msgid "Atho tiracchānagatāpi ekadā,"
msgstr "Then sometimes we become animals,"

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "thag19.1:42.4"
msgid "Petattanaṃ vāpi taveva vāhasā."
msgstr "and life as a ghost is also on account of you."

#. HTML: </p><p><a class="sc" id="39"></a><a class="vns" id="vns1132"></a><a
#. class="vnp" id="vnp1129"></a>
msgctxt "thag19.1:43.1"
msgid "Nanu dubbhissasi maṃ punappunaṃ,"
msgstr "Come what may, you won’t betray me again,"

#. HTML: <br>
#. VAR: cāraṇikaṃva → vāraṇikaṃva (s2, s3, pts1)
#. VAR: dassayaṃ → dussahaṃ (s2, s3) | dassahaṃ (pts1)
msgctxt "thag19.1:43.2"
msgid "Muhuṃ muhuṃ cāraṇikaṃva dassayaṃ;"
msgstr "dazzling me with your ever-changing display!"

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "thag19.1:43.3"
msgid "Ummattakeneva mayā palobhasi,"
msgstr "You play with me like I’m mad—"

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "thag19.1:43.4"
msgid "Kiñcāpi te citta virādhitaṃ mayā."
msgstr "but how have I ever failed you, mind?"

#. HTML: </p><p><a class="sc" id="40"></a><a class="vns" id="vns1133"></a><a
#. class="vnp" id="vnp1130"></a>
msgctxt "thag19.1:44.1"
msgid "Idaṃ pure cittamacāri cārikaṃ,"
msgstr "In the past my mind wandered"

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "thag19.1:44.2"
msgid "Yenicchakaṃ yatthakāmaṃ yathāsukhaṃ;"
msgstr "how it wished, where it liked, as it pleased."

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "thag19.1:44.3"
msgid "Tadajjahaṃ niggahessāmi yoniso,"
msgstr "Now I’ll carefully guide it,"

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "thag19.1:44.4"
msgid "Hatthippabhinnaṃ viya aṅkusaggaho."
msgstr "as a trainer with a hook guides a rutting elephant."

#. HTML: </p><p><a class="sc" id="41"></a><a class="vns" id="vns1134"></a><a
#. class="vnp" id="vnp1131"></a>
msgctxt "thag19.1:45.1"
msgid "Satthā ca me lokamimaṃ adhiṭṭhahi,"
msgstr "The teacher willed that this world appear to me"

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "thag19.1:45.2"
msgid "Aniccato addhuvato asārato;"
msgstr "as impermanent, unstable, insubstantial."

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "thag19.1:45.3"
msgid "Pakkhanda maṃ citta jinassa sāsane,"
msgstr "Mind, let me leap into the victor’s teaching,"

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "thag19.1:45.4"
msgid "Tārehi oghā mahatā suduttarā."
msgstr "carry me over the great flood, so hard to pass."

#. HTML: </p><p><a class="sc" id="42"></a><a class="vns" id="vns1135"></a><a
#. class="vnp" id="vnp1132"></a>
msgctxt "thag19.1:46.1"
msgid "Na te idaṃ citta yathā purāṇakaṃ,"
msgstr "Things have changed, mind!"

#. HTML: <br>
#. VAR: vase nivattituṃ → vasena vattituṃ (?)
msgctxt "thag19.1:46.2"
msgid "Nāhaṃ alaṃ tuyha vase nivattituṃ;"
msgstr "Nothing could make me return to your control!"

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "thag19.1:46.3"
msgid "Mahesino pabbajitomhi sāsane,"
msgstr "I’ve gone forth in the teaching of the great hermit,"

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "thag19.1:46.4"
msgid "Na mādisā honti vināsadhārino."
msgstr "those like me don’t come to ruin."

#. HTML: </p><p><a class="sc" id="43"></a><a class="vns" id="vns1136"></a><a
#. class="vnp" id="vnp1133"></a><a class="pts" id="pts102"></a>
msgctxt "thag19.1:47.1"
msgid "Nagā samuddā saritā vasundharā,"
msgstr "Mountains, oceans, rivers, the earth;"

#. HTML: <br>
#. VAR: adho divā → adhodisā (s2, s3, pts1)
msgctxt "thag19.1:47.2"
msgid "Disā catasso vidisā adho divā;"
msgstr "the four directions, the intermediate directions, below and in the sky;"

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "thag19.1:47.3"
msgid "Sabbe aniccā tibhavā upaddutā,"
msgstr "the three realms of existence are all impermanent and troubled—"

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "thag19.1:47.4"
msgid "Kuhiṃ gato citta sukhaṃ ramissasi."
msgstr "where can you go to find happiness, mind?"

#. HTML: </p><p><a class="sc" id="44"></a><a class="vns" id="vns1137"></a><a
#. class="vnp" id="vnp1134"></a>
#. VAR: Dhitipparaṃ → dhī dhī paraṃ (s2, s3, pts1)
msgctxt "thag19.1:48.1"
msgid "Dhitipparaṃ kiṃ mama citta kāhisi,"
msgstr "Mind, what will you do to someone who has made the ultimate commitment?"

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "thag19.1:48.2"
msgid "Na te alaṃ citta vasānuvattako;"
msgstr "Nothing could make me a follower under your control, mind;"

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "thag19.1:48.3"
msgid "Na jātu bhastaṃ ubhatomukhaṃ chupe,"
msgstr "there’s no way I’d touch a bellows with a mouth open at each end;"

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "thag19.1:48.4"
msgid "Dhiratthu pūraṃ nava sotasandaniṃ."
msgstr "curse this mortal frame flowing with nine streams!"

#. HTML: </p><p><a class="sc" id="45"></a><a class="vns" id="vns1138"></a><a
#. class="vnp" id="vnp1135"></a>
msgctxt "thag19.1:49.1"
msgid "Varāhaeṇeyyavigāḷhasevite,"
msgstr "You’ve ascended the mountain peak, full of nature’s beauty,"

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "thag19.1:49.2"
msgid "Pabbhārakuṭṭe pakateva sundare;"
msgstr "frequented by boars and antelopes,"

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "thag19.1:49.3"
msgid "Navambunā pāvusasitthakānane,"
msgstr "a grove sprinkled with fresh water in the rains;"

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "thag19.1:49.4"
msgid "Tahiṃ guhāgehagato ramissasi."
msgstr "and there you’ll be happy in your cave-home."

#. HTML: </p><p><a class="sc" id="46"></a><a class="vns" id="vns1139"></a><a
#. class="vnp" id="vnp1136"></a>
msgctxt "thag19.1:50.1"
msgid "Sunīlagīvā susikhā supekhunā,"
msgstr "Peacocks with beautiful necks and crests,"

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "thag19.1:50.2"
msgid "Sucittapattacchadanā vihaṅgamā;"
msgstr "colorful tail-feathers and wings,"

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "thag19.1:50.3"
msgid "Sumañjughosatthanitābhigajjino,"
msgstr "crying out at the resounding thunder:"

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "thag19.1:50.4"
msgid "Te taṃ ramessanti vanamhi jhāyinaṃ."
msgstr "they’ll delight you as you meditate in the forest."

#. HTML: </p><p><a class="sc" id="47"></a><a class="vns" id="vns1140"></a><a
#. class="vnp" id="vnp1137"></a>
msgctxt "thag19.1:51.1"
msgid "Vuṭṭhamhi deve caturaṅgule tiṇe,"
msgstr "When the sky has rained down, and the grass is four inches high,"

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "thag19.1:51.2"
msgid "Sampupphite meghanibhamhi kānane;"
msgstr "and the grove is full of flowers like a cloud,"

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "thag19.1:51.3"
msgid "Nagantare viṭapisamo sayissaṃ,"
msgstr "in the mountain cleft, like the fork of a tree, I’ll lie;"

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "thag19.1:51.4"
msgid "Taṃ me mudū hehiti tūlasannibhaṃ."
msgstr "it will be as soft as cotton-buds."

#. HTML: </p><p><a class="sc" id="48"></a><a class="vns" id="vns1141"></a><a
#. class="vnp" id="vnp1138"></a>
msgctxt "thag19.1:52.1"
msgid "Tathā tu kassāmi yathāpi issaro,"
msgstr "I’ll act as a master does:"

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "thag19.1:52.2"
msgid "Yaṃ labbhati tenapi hotu me alaṃ;"
msgstr "let whatever I get be enough for me."

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "thag19.1:52.3"
msgid "Na tāhaṃ kassāmi yathā atandito,"
msgstr "And that’s why I’ll make you as supple"

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "thag19.1:52.4"
msgid "Biḷārabhastaṃva yathā sumadditaṃ."
msgstr "as a tireless worker makes a cat-skin bag."

#. HTML: </p><p><a class="sc" id="49"></a><a class="vns" id="vns1142"></a><a
#. class="vnp" id="vnp1139"></a>
msgctxt "thag19.1:53.1"
msgid "Tathā tu kassāmi yathāpi issaro,"
msgstr "I’ll act as a master does:"

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "thag19.1:53.2"
msgid "Yaṃ labbhati tenapi hotu me alaṃ;"
msgstr "let whatever I get be enough for me."

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "thag19.1:53.3"
msgid "Viriyena taṃ mayha vasānayissaṃ,"
msgstr "I’ll control you with my energy,"

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "thag19.1:53.4"
msgid "Gajaṃva mattaṃ kusalaṅkusaggaho."
msgstr "as a skilled trainer controls an elephant with a hook."

#. HTML: </p><p><a class="sc" id="50"></a><a class="vns" id="vns1143"></a><a
#. class="vnp" id="vnp1140"></a>
msgctxt "thag19.1:54.1"
msgid "Tayā sudantena avaṭṭhitena hi,"
msgstr "Now that you’re well-tamed and reliable,"

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "thag19.1:54.2"
msgid "Hayena yoggācariyova ujjunā;"
msgstr "I can use you, like a trainer uses a straight-running horse,"

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "thag19.1:54.3"
msgid "Pahomi maggaṃ paṭipajjituṃ sivaṃ,"
msgstr "to practice the path so full of grace,"

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "thag19.1:54.4"
msgid "Cittānurakkhīhi sadā nisevitaṃ."
msgstr "cultivated by those who take care of their minds."

#. HTML: </p><p><a class="sc" id="51"></a><a class="vns" id="vns1144"></a><a
#. class="vnp" id="vnp1141"></a><a class="pts" id="pts103"></a>
msgctxt "thag19.1:55.1"
msgid "Ārammaṇe taṃ balasā nibandhisaṃ,"
msgstr "I shall strongly fasten you to a meditation subject,"

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "thag19.1:55.2"
msgid "Nāgaṃva thambhamhi daḷhāya rajjuyā;"
msgstr "as an elephant is tied to a post with firm rope."

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "thag19.1:55.3"
msgid "Taṃ me suguttaṃ satiyā subhāvitaṃ,"
msgstr "You’ll be well-guarded by me, well-developed by mindfulness,"

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "thag19.1:55.4"
msgid "Anissitaṃ sabbabhavesu hehisi."
msgstr "and unattached to rebirth in all states of existence."

#. HTML: </p><p><a class="sc" id="52"></a><a class="vns" id="vns1145"></a><a
#. class="vnp" id="vnp1142"></a>
msgctxt "thag19.1:56.1"
msgid "Paññāya chetvā vipathānusārinaṃ,"
msgstr "You’ll use understanding to cut the follower of the wrong path,"

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "thag19.1:56.2"
msgid "Yogena niggayha pathe nivesiya;"
msgstr "restrain them by practice, and settle them on the right path."

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "thag19.1:56.3"
msgid "Disvā samudayaṃ vibhavañca sambhavaṃ,"
msgstr "And when you have seen the cause of suffering arise and pass away,"

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "thag19.1:56.4"
msgid "Dāyādako hehisi aggavādino."
msgstr "you’ll be an heir to the greatest teacher."

#. HTML: </p><p><a class="sc" id="53"></a><a class="vns" id="vns1146"></a><a
#. class="vnp" id="vnp1143"></a>
msgctxt "thag19.1:57.1"
msgid "Catubbipallāsavasaṃ adhiṭṭhitaṃ,"
msgstr "Under the sway of the four distortions, mind,"

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "thag19.1:57.2"
msgid "Gāmaṇḍalaṃva parinesi citta maṃ;"
msgstr "you dragged me around like a bull in a pit;"

#. HTML: <br>
#. VAR: Nanu → nūna (bj) | na nūna (pts2)
msgctxt "thag19.1:57.3"
msgid "Nanu saṃyojanabandhanacchidaṃ,"
msgstr "but now you won’t associate with the great sage of compassion,"

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "thag19.1:57.4"
msgid "Saṃsevase kāruṇikaṃ mahāmuniṃ."
msgstr "the cutter of fetters and bonds?"

#. HTML: </p><p><a class="sc" id="54"></a><a class="vns" id="vns1147"></a><a
#. class="vnp" id="vnp1144"></a>
msgctxt "thag19.1:58.1"
msgid "Migo yathā seri sucittakānane,"
msgstr "Like a deer roaming free in the colorful forest,"

#. HTML: <br>
#. VAR: pāvusaabbhamāliniṃ → pāvisi abbhamālinaṃ (s2, s3, pts1-2) | ... māliṃ
#. (?)
msgctxt "thag19.1:58.2"
msgid "Rammaṃ giriṃ pāvusaabbhamāliniṃ;"
msgstr "I’ll ascend the lovely mountain wreathed in cloud,"

#. HTML: <br>
#. VAR: ramissaṃ → ramissasi (s2, s3, pts1-2, mr)
msgctxt "thag19.1:58.3"
msgid "Anākule tattha nage ramissaṃ,"
msgstr "and rejoice to be on that hill, free of folk—"

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "thag19.1:58.4"
msgid "Asaṃsayaṃ citta parā bhavissasi."
msgstr "there is no doubt you’ll perish, mind."

#. HTML: </p><p><a class="sc" id="55"></a><a class="vns" id="vns1148"></a><a
#. class="vnp" id="vnp1145"></a>
msgctxt "thag19.1:59.1"
msgid "Ye tuyha chandena vasena vattino,"
msgstr "The men and women who live under your will and command,"

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "thag19.1:59.2"
msgid "Narā ca nārī ca anubhonti yaṃ sukhaṃ;"
msgstr "whatever pleasure they experience,"

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "thag19.1:59.3"
msgid "Aviddasū māravasānuvattino,"
msgstr "they are ignorant and fall under Māra’s control;"

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "thag19.1:59.4"
msgid "Bhavābhinandī tava citta sāvakā”ti."
msgstr "loving life, they’re your disciples, mind."

#. HTML: </p></blockquote><p class="endsutta">
msgctxt "thag19.1:60.1"
msgid "…"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "thag19.1:60.2"
msgid "Tālapuṭo thero …."
msgstr ""

#. HTML: </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "thag19.1:61.1"
msgid "Paññāsanipāto niṭṭhito."
msgstr ""

#. HTML: </p><p class="uddana">
msgctxt "thag19.1:62.1"
msgid "Tatruddānaṃ"
msgstr ""

#. HTML: </p><blockquote class="uddanagatha"><p><a class="sc" id="56"></a>
msgctxt "thag19.1:63.1"
msgid "Paññāsamhi nipātamhi,"
msgstr ""

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "thag19.1:63.2"
msgid "eko tālapuṭo suci;"
msgstr ""

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "thag19.1:63.3"
msgid "Gāthāyo tattha paññāsa,"
msgstr ""

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "thag19.1:63.4"
msgid "puna pañca ca uttarīti."
msgstr ""
